|                |
|Spaghetti Recipe|
|                |

Ingredients
-Spaghetti Noodles of your choice
-Tomato Sauce
-Mushrooms (Optional)
-Onions (Optional)
-Meatballs (Optional)
Steps
1. Boil the noodles in a pot of boiling water (10 Minutes)
2. Place meat in a skillet and let it cook until it turns brown
3. Once the meat is finished add the sauce to it
4. Add the extra mushrooms and onions into the meat/sauce pan
5. Take out your noodles and put them somewhere you can pour stuff onto, like a plate.
6. Pour the sauce on  your noodles and enjoy your spaghet

